description: 'The First 365' is a collection of works from my first year creating art every single day. This token shows every piece of art from the entire year in rapid succession together to commemorate the work that went into creating the body of work and the creative evolution that took place. It is a celebration of hard work but also of all the love, and support that helped me to accomplish this giant personal milestone. It is a giant thank you to everyone who helped me along the way and made it all worthwhile. I couldn't have done it without you. <3
